'''Hayat Music TV''' is a [[music television]] channel from [[Hayat TV (Bosnia and Herzegovina)|Hayat TV]] that broadcasting [[music videos]] available via [[cable systems]] in [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]] and [[Socialist Federal Republic of Yugoslavia|former Yugoslavia]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ekskluziva.ba/vijest-3595 www.ekskluziva.ba |title=Hayat danas slavi 20 godina rada! |publisher=ekskluziva.ba |date=2012-02-24 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029185416/http://www.ekskluziva.ba/vijest-3595 |archivedate=2013-10-29 |df= }}</ref>
